Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 485
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=Repentance, Renewal and Awakening
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
Devotee： What does Maharshi say about Hatha Yoga or Tantric
practices?

Maharshi： Maharshi does not criticise any of the existing methods.
All are good for the purification of the mind. Because the purified
mind alone is capable of grasping his method and sticking to its
practice.
